comments: Beverley (LAC) is in his legally obtained position when he absorbs the incidental contact that is initiated by Harden (HOU).
Chandler (HOU) makes marginal contact to Harrell's (LAC) arm but the contact does not affect his ability to make his desired pass.
Williams (LAC) briefly grasps Rivers' (HOU) arm as he gets in position to receive the pass but the contact is marginal.
Williams (LAC) gathers on his right foot when he receives the pass and takes more than two steps.
Rivers (HOU) maintains a legal guarding position and absorbs the contact from Williams (LAC) at the end of the drive.
Chandler (HOU) establishes himself in a legal screening position in Harkless' (LAC) path and gives him room to avoid the contact.

During their timeout called at 1:31, LAC is told that they had been misinformed that they would retain a timeout called earlier at Q4 4:35 in conjunction with an attempted coach's challenge and that they were now out of timeouts.
All technical fouls are reviewed by League Operations.
All technical fouls are reviewed by League Operations.
During the screen, Tucker (HOU) and Leonard (LAC) engage and disengage and the contact is marginal.
Williams (LAC) establishes himself in a legal screening position in Tucker's (HOU) path and gives him room to avoid the contact.
Harkless (LAC) cleanly dislodges the ball before it bounces off of Westbrook's (HOU) foot.
Harrell (LAC) makes contact to Westbrook's (HOU) arm during his shooting motion that affects his driving shot attempt.
Harrell (LAC) establishes himself in a screening position as he briefly engages and disengages with  Rivers (HOU).
Westbrook (HOU) maintains a legal guarding position on Williams (LAC) before he makes his pass.
Harden (HOU) maintains a legal guarding position on Leonard (LAC) and cleanly dislodges the ball.
Leonard (LAC) makes marginal contact to Harden's (HOU) body as he brings the ball up the court but the contact does not affect his SQBR.
Harkless (LAC) moves laterally into Harden's (HOU) path as he brings the ball up the court.
Chandler (HOU) maintains a legal guarding position during the driving shot attempt by Mann (LAC).
